      <title>Ysgol Llanilar Workshop 1</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/260324-llanilar-workshop-1/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 20:19:33 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/260324-llanilar-workshop-1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NB:&lt;/strong&gt; The notes before Easter have been written in retrospect, which means they lack detail. In future, I’ll be writing notes immediately afterwards, and also asking for immediate &amp;amp; short feedback from students and participants.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;iframe width=&#34;425&#34; height=&#34;350&#34; src=&#34;https://www.openstreetmap.org/export/embed.html?bbox=-4.028227329254151%2C52.35499535531641%2C-4.0140652656555185%2C52.36095802129768&amp;amp;layer=mapnik&#34; style=&#34;border: 1px solid black&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.openstreetmap.org/?#map=17/52.357977/-4.021146&amp;amp;layers=N&#34;&gt;View Larger Map&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;oriel-gallery&#34;&gt;Oriel Gallery&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gallery caption-position-bottom caption-effect-slide hover-effect-zoom hover-transition&#34; itemscope itemtype=&#34;http://schema.org/ImageGallery&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;  &#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;link rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; href=http://localhost:1313/css/hugo-easy-gallery.css /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34; &gt;&#xA;    &lt;figure  itemprop=&#34;associatedMedia&#34; itemscope itemtype=&#34;http://schema.org/ImageObject&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;img&#34; style=&#34;background-image: url(&#39;https://res.cloudinary.com/naturceredigion/image/upload/v1774816007/250324-llanilar-workshop1-lichen.jpg&#39;);&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img itemprop=&#34;thumbnail&#34; src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/naturceredigion/image/upload/v1774816007/250324-llanilar-workshop1-lichen.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Looking at lichen (a symbiotic life form of fungi and algae/bacteria) with a hand lens went down very well in the classroom&#34;/&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/naturceredigion/image/upload/v1774816007/250324-llanilar-workshop1-lichen.jpg&#34; itemprop=&#34;contentUrl&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;        &lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;            &lt;p&gt;Looking at lichen (a symbiotic life form of fungi and algae/bacteria) with a hand lens went down very well in the classroom&lt;/p&gt;</description>
